description: Delirious Hunter is back at the dungeon eagerly anticipating her next round of training under the stern hand of Master Joseph. Starting with her bent over a large oak crate dressed only in stockings, Master warms her up with some sensual spanking and sensation play and then moves on to a series of impact games in which she chooses each toy and submits to its fierce impact until she can take no more, and then chooses the next implement. After all are finished, Delirious is rewarded by being given permission to give Master a great hand and blowjob.
title: A New Sex and Submission Game for Delirious Hunter
